{"id": "1288213816144040056", "channel_id": "1288213816144040056", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "不可避免的用了几个活动SR，最难凹的是1-4和3-4。因为省去了道中，让蜘蛛可以直接跳到王关，但是图鲁多段对死抗要求极高，菲茵特加到860%多还是赌了6次死抗，而且只能图速度不能图质量，宁菲亚和湖畔回眸都省不了，其次是1-4，朵尔的等价交换和莉兹的绿炎打架头疼的要命，最后还是用魔术师达成了平衡。其他三队深海都超级轻松～（所以什么界域最轮椅知道了么），自己凯刻斯练度不足就借了一个高练的。\n\n所以说不要纠结限定的强度了！全常驻都能融灾375了！只用抽XP就好了！<:Coffee:1240919421791375380> <:Coffee:1240919421791375380> <:Coffee:1240919421791375380>", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T19:01:47.624000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-09-25T00:31:50.092000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1288213816751947796", "filename": "Screenshot_20240925_010729_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 213745, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288213816144040056/1288213816751947796/Screenshot_20240925_010729_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb901b&is=69fa3e9b&hm=0c4da4abe93702f600c1205d1d2b63dcc3d5508ed29fd4f4edbdb758cd38365f&"}, {"id": "1288213817104273458", "filename": "Screenshot_20240924_225405_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 220163, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288213816144040056/1288213817104273458/Screenshot_20240924_225405_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb901b&is=69fa3e9b&hm=c33f4b399b7914be0783e3ad4cfe7b98b15075e1c49251c2a305d695e2b3ff5e&"}, {"id": "1288213817498538055", "filename": "Screenshot_20240924_213329_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 217455, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288213816144040056/1288213817498538055/Screenshot_20240924_213329_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb901b&is=69fa3e9b&hm=f2e7036b83e0955f8c5f92298f37a8f4ef5af2e47157d9a076e2cad4711f60eb&"}, {"id": "1288213817922424895", "filename": "Screenshot_20240925_025338_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg"